name: [LoCon/LoRA] Airconditioner/空调 Style
description:
This is a LoCon model trained from 87 images about flatcolor small town background,the bright colors are reminiscent of air conditioning,and that's where the name comes from.

You can use the locon to design town,wilderness,don't forget flowers

Weight 1.0 will perform better.
